#: ../../interaction.rst:2
msgid "与 AgentSociety 交互"
msgstr "Interacting with AgentSociety"

#: ../../interaction.rst:4
msgid "本指南介绍如何在实验期间与 AgentSociety 2 交互。"
msgstr "This guide introduces how to interact with AgentSociety 2 during experiments."

#: ../../interaction.rst:7
msgid "概述"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../interaction.rst:9
msgid "AgentSociety 2 提供两种主要的交互模式："
msgstr "AgentSociety 2 provides two main interaction modes:"

#: ../../interaction.rst:11
msgid "**查询模式** (只读): 提问而不修改模拟状态"
msgstr "**Query Mode** (read-only): Ask questions without modifying simulation state"

#: ../../interaction.rst:12
msgid "**干预模式** (读写): 修改智能体状态或环境变量"
msgstr "**Intervention Mode** (read-write): Modify agent state or environment variables"

#: ../../interaction.rst:14
msgid "这些交互可以在以下时间执行："
msgstr "These interactions can be performed at:"

#: ../../interaction.rst:16
msgid "**模拟期间**: 在步骤之间或特定时间点"
msgstr "**During simulation**: Between steps or at specific time points"

#: ../../interaction.rst:17
msgid "**模拟后**: 查询最终状态或收集调查数据"
msgstr "**After simulation**: Query final state or collect survey data"

#: ../../interaction.rst:20
msgid "基本交互模式"
msgstr "Basic Interaction Patterns"

#: ../../interaction.rst:23
msgid "ask() 方法 - 只读查询"
msgstr "ask() Method - Read-only Queries"

#: ../../interaction.rst:25
msgid "使用 ``society.ask()`` 进行不修改模拟的只读查询："
msgstr "Use ``society.ask()`` for read-only queries that don't modify the simulation:"

#: ../../interaction.rst:39
msgid "intervene() 方法 - 读写修改"
msgstr "intervene() Method - Read-Write Modifications"

#: ../../interaction.rst:41
msgid "使用 ``society.intervene()`` 对模拟进行更改："
msgstr "Use ``society.intervene()`` to make changes to the simulation:"

#: ../../interaction.rst:61
msgid "模拟工作流程"
msgstr "Simulation Workflow"

#: ../../interaction.rst:64
msgid "使用逐步控制运行"
msgstr "Running with Step Control"

#: ../../interaction.rst:94
msgid "使用时间控制运行"
msgstr "Running with Time Control"

#: ../../interaction.rst:108
msgid "数据收集"
msgstr "Data Collection"

#: ../../interaction.rst:111
msgid "收集智能体响应"
msgstr "Collecting Agent Responses"

#: ../../interaction.rst:135
msgid "使用 ReplayWriter 进行数据收集"
msgstr "Data Collection with ReplayWriter"

#: ../../interaction.rst:163
msgid "常见交互场景"
msgstr "Common Interaction Scenarios"

#: ../../interaction.rst:166
msgid "场景 1: 事件干预"
msgstr "Scenario 1: Event Intervention"

#: ../../interaction.rst:186
msgid "场景 2: 政策实验"
msgstr "Scenario 2: Policy Experiments"

#: ../../interaction.rst:213
msgid "场景 3: 多个时间点收集数据"
msgstr "Scenario 3: Data Collection at Multiple Time Points"

#: ../../interaction.rst:234
msgid "最佳实践"
msgstr "Best Practices"

#: ../../interaction.rst:236
msgid "**对查询使用 ask()**: 只需要信息时始终使用 ``ask()``"
msgstr "**Use ask() for queries**: Always use ``ask()`` when you only need information"

#: ../../interaction.rst:238
msgid "**对更改使用 intervene()**: 只在想修改状态时使用 ``intervene()``"
msgstr "**Use intervene() for changes**: Only use ``intervene()`` when you want to modify state"

#: ../../interaction.rst:240
msgid "**结合 ReplayWriter**: 启用回放记录以进行全面的数据收集"
msgstr "**Combine with ReplayWriter**: Enable replay recording for comprehensive data collection"

#: ../../interaction.rst:242
msgid "**查询特定智能体**: 向特定智能体提问以获得有针对性的响应"
msgstr "**Query specific agents**: Ask specific agents for targeted responses"

#: ../../interaction.rst:244
msgid "**适时干预**: 在适当的模拟时间进行干预以获得现实效果"
msgstr "**Intervene at appropriate times**: Intervene at appropriate simulation times for realistic effects"

#: ../../interaction.rst:57
msgid "交互模式对比"
msgstr "Interaction Mode Comparison"
